REGAIN 5% OF HIS HEALTH PER GAME TURN.

RESTING PLAYERS; IF A WOUNDED PLAYER `SITS OUT` A MISSION HE WILL BE FULLY
HEALED,READY FOR THE NEXT MISSION.

